    "# 🧠 Context Window Impact Study — LSTM\n",
    "**Generative AI Lab | OEL Project**  \n",
    "**Team:** Saad Ul Hassan, Abdul Rafay  \n",
    "**Date:** April 20, 2026\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "This notebook systematically investigates how **sequence length (context window size)** impacts LSTM performance across:\n",
    "- Prediction Accuracy / Cross-Entropy Loss\n",
    "- Training Time per epoch\n",
    "- GPU Memory Consumption\n",
    "- Context Retention Score (long-range dependency resolution)\n",
    "\n",
    "**Configurations tested:**\n",
    "| Config | Sequence Length | Description |\n",
    "|--------|----------------|-------------|\n",
    "| C1 | 10–20 | Short — baseline |\n",
    "| C2 | 50–100 | Medium — balanced |\n",
    "| C3 | 200–500 | Long — rich context |\n",
    "| C4 | 500+ | Very Long — stress test |"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 📦 1. Install & Import Dependencies"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
